# Rust build output
/app/target

# Minecraft art is Mojang's and is not redistributed here. The `minecraft-assets`
# Nix derivation extracts it from the official client jar; the Nix build copies it
# into each crate before compiling, and `app/scripts/fetch-assets.sh` does the
# same for local `cargo` builds. See packages/minecraft-assets.
/app/crates/*/assets/*.png
/app/crates/*/assets/**/*.png

